author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a wild ARG on the Deep Web where a group of people are selling shoes that could have belonged to those long departed, a site that has some budding game developers and even an old group of demon worshippers who have rebranded. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: I Found A "Bloody" Boot On Deep Web 243...
